Jewellery ERP & Girvi Management Platform

Reports & Analytics Module Specification v1.0

Module Code: MOD-REPORTS
Priority: High
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Customer Module, Girvi Module, Interest Module, Vault Module, Compliance Module, Staff Module, Dashboard Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Reports & Analytics Module provides operational, financial, compliance, audit, and business intelligence reporting for the entire Jewellery ERP.

This module acts as the central data intelligence layer of the platform.

Responsibilities:

* Financial Reports
* Girvi Reports
* Interest Reports
* Collection Reports
* Vault Reports
* Customer Reports
* Staff Activity Reports
* Compliance Reports
* Audit Reports
* Business Analytics
* Export Engine

