6. Core Business Rules

BR-REP-001

Reports must be read-only.

BR-REP-002

Exports must include audit metadata.

BR-REP-003

Tenant data isolation mandatory.

BR-REP-004

Financial reports must reconcile with ledger.

BR-REP-005

Report generation logged.

BR-REP-006

Sensitive reports restricted by RBAC.

BR-REP-007

Historical reports immutable.

BR-REP-008

Exports watermark with tenant details.

