⸻

Collection Efficiency Formula

Collection\ Efficiency = \frac{Collected\ Amount}{Due\ Amount} \times 100

⸻

Redemption Rate Formula

Redemption\ Rate = \frac{Redeemed\ Accounts}{Total\ Accounts} \times 100

⸻

Vault Utilization Formula

Vault\ Utilization = \frac{Occupied\ Slots}{Total\ Slots} \times 100

